## UITool.unregisterAll() method

Remove all elements created by `createElement`<!-- -->.

**Signature:**

```typescript
unregisterAll(): void;
```
**Returns:**

void

## Remarks

&gt; What is this for?

In bootstrap plugins, elements must be manually maintained and removed on exiting.

This API does this for you.
